Package ch.iserver.ace.net.protocol

The package ch.iserver.ace.net.protocol contains the protocol implementation which itself makes use of the BEEP framework.

          Description

Interface Summary
Deserializer Interface for the deserialization of messages using a ParserHandler.
ProtocolConstants This interface declares constants for the protocol implementation of ACE.
Request The interface Request is used for message processing, i.e.
Serializer Interface Serializer to serialize requests according to some data desccription language.
 

Class Summary
AbstractConnection AbstractConnection contains all common functionality for a connection.
BEEPSessionListener BEEPSessionListener listens repeatedly for sessions initiated by other users.
BEEPSessionListenerFactory Factory to create instances of BEEPSessionListener.
CollaborationDeserializer Implementation of Deserializer.
CollaborationParserHandler CollaborationParserHandler for the parsing of messages.
CollaborationSerializer Serializes XML messages used in a collaborative session.

MainConnection Wrapper/Decorator class around a Channel.

ParticipantConnectionImpl The ParticipantConnectionImpl represents a connection from the publisher of a document to a participant.
ParticipantConnectionImplFactory Factory class to create instances of ParticipantConnectionImpl.

ProfileRegistryFactory The ProfileRegistryFactory creates the ProfileRegistry.
QueryInfo QueryInfo is a pure helper class used by the ResponseParserHandler to parse and construct the response objects, respectively.
RemoteUserSession The RemoteUserSession includes the session and connection management for a remote user.

SerializerImpl Default implementation for interface Serializer.
SessionCleanup Command object used to clean up a session and to release its resources.
SessionConnectionImpl SessionConnectionImpl represents a session connection from a particpant to the publisher of a shared document.
SessionManager The SessionManager is the central class that keeps all RemoteUserSession objects managed in a central place.

SessionRequestHandlerFactory Factory class to create instances of SessionRequestHandler.
StartChannelListenerImpl BEEP Core specific class to receive notifications when a Channel is started or closed.
TLVHandler The TLVHandler encodes and decodes a PortableDocument to TLV.

ProtocolException The ProtocolException is thrown on protocol failures, i.e.
RecoveryException RecoveryException is thrown by the AbstractConnection.recover() method to indicate that the recovery failed.
SerializeException SerializeException is thrown if an erro during serialization occurs.
